   - Total Assets = $29,133,140.32
   - ROA = $405,999.64 / $29,133,140.32 × 100% = 1.39%

4. **Accounts Receivable Turnover Ratio** = Net Credit Sales / Average Accounts Receivable
   - Net Credit Sales = Total Revenue = $14,542,813.42

   - Accounts Receivable Turnover Ratio = $14,542,813.42 / $5,110,723.68 = 2.85
